{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"The big residual"},{"time":2000,"text":"is always value for money."},{"time":4000,"text":"All the time we are trying to get value for money."},{"time":7000,"text":"What we don't look for"},{"time":9000,"text":"is value for many,"},{"time":11000,"text":"while we are generating value for money."},{"time":14000,"text":"Do we care about those four billion people"},{"time":16000,"text":"whose income levels are less than two dollars a day,"},{"time":18000,"text":"the so-called bottom of the pyramid?"},{"time":21000,"text":"What are the challenges in getting value for money"},{"time":24000,"text":"as well as value for many?"},{"time":26000,"text":"We have described here"},{"time":28000,"text":"in terms of the performance"},{"time":30000,"text":"and the price."},{"time":32000,"text":"If you have money, of course, you can get the value."},{"time":35000,"text":"You can get a Mercedes"},{"time":37000,"text":"for a very high price,"},{"time":39000,"text":"very high performance."},{"time":41000,"text":"But if you don't have money, what happens?"},{"time":44000,"text":"Well, you are to ride a bicycle,"},{"time":46000,"text":"carrying your own weight and also some other weight,"},{"time":49000,"text":"so that you can earn the bread for the day."},{"time":52000,"text":"Well, poor do not remain poor;"},{"time":54000,"text":"they become lower-middle-class."},{"time":56000,"text":"And if they do so,"},{"time":58000,"text":"then, of course, the conditions improve,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and they start riding on scooters."},{"time":63000,"text":"But the challenge is, again, they don't get much value,"},{"time":66000,"text":"because they can't afford anything more than the scooter."},{"time":70000,"text":"The issue is, at that price,"},{"time":72000,"text":"can you give them some extra value?"},{"time":75000,"text":"A super value,"},{"time":77000,"text":"in terms of their ability to ride in a car,"},{"time":79000,"text":"to get that dignity, to get that safety,"},{"time":82000,"text":"looks practically impossible, isn't it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":85000,"text":"Now, this is something"},{"time":87000,"text":"that we see on Indian streets"},{"time":89000,"text":"all the time."},{"time":91000,"text":"But many people see the same thing"},{"time":93000,"text":"and think things differently,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and one of them is here, Ratan Tata."},{"time":101000,"text":"The great thing about our leaders"},{"time":103000,"text":"is that, should they not only have passion in their belly,"},{"time":107000,"text":"which practically all of them have,"},{"time":109000,"text":"they're also very innovative."},{"time":111000,"text":"An innovator is one who does not know it cannot be done."},{"time":114000,"text":"They believe that things can be done."},{"time":116000,"text":"But great leaders like Ratan"},{"time":118000,"text":"have compassion."},{"time":120000,"text":"And what you said, Lakshmi, is absolutely true:"},{"time":122000,"text":"it's not just Ratan Tata,"},{"time":124000,"text":"it's the house of Tatas over time."},{"time":126000,"text":"Let me confirm what she said."},{"time":128000,"text":"Yes, I went barefoot"},{"time":131000,"text":"until I was 12."},{"time":133000,"text":"I struggled to [unclear] day"},{"time":135000,"text":"was a huge issue."},{"time":137000,"text":"And when I finished my SSC, the eleventh standard,"},{"time":140000,"text":"I stood eleventh among 125,000 students."},{"time":143000,"text":"But I was about to leave the school,"},{"time":145000,"text":"because my poor mother couldn't afford schooling."},{"time":147000,"text":"And it was [unclear] Tata Trust, which gave me six rupees per month,"},{"time":150000,"text":"almost a dollar per month for six years."},{"time":153000,"text":"That's how I'm standing before you."},{"time":155000,"text":"So that is the House of Tata."},{"time":157000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":160000,"text":"Innovation, compassion and passion."},{"time":162000,"text":"They combine all that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"And it was that compassion which bothered them,"},{"time":167000,"text":"because when he saw -- in fact, he told me about eight or nine years ago"},{"time":170000,"text":"how he was driving his own car --"},{"time":173000,"text":"he drives his own car by the way --"},{"time":176000,"text":"and he saw in the rain,"},{"time":178000,"text":"a family like the one that I showed to you"},{"time":180000,"text":"getting drenched with an infant."},{"time":182000,"text":"And then he said, \"Well, I must give them a car that they can afford,"},{"time":185000,"text":"one lakh car, $2,000 car.\""},{"time":188000,"text":"Of course, as soon as you say something like this"},{"time":190000,"text":"people say it is impossible,"},{"time":192000,"text":"and that's what was said by Suzuki."},{"time":194000,"text":"He said, oh, probably he is going to build a three-wheeler"},{"time":197000,"text":"with stepney."},{"time":199000,"text":"And you can see the cartoon here."},{"time":201000,"text":"Well they didn't build that. They built a proper car. Nano."},{"time":205000,"text":"And mind you, I'm six feet half an inch,"},{"time":207000,"text":"Ratan is taller than me,"},{"time":209000,"text":"and we have ample space in the front"},{"time":212000,"text":"and ample space in the back in this particular car."},{"time":215000,"text":"And incredible car."},{"time":217000,"text":"And of course, nothing succeeds like success;"},{"time":220000,"text":"the cynics then turned around,"},{"time":223000,"text":"and one after the other"},{"time":225000,"text":"they also started saying, \"Yes, we also want to make a car in the Nano Segment."},{"time":228000,"text":"We'll manufacture a car in the Nano Segment.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":231000,"text":"How did this great story unfold,"},{"time":234000,"text":"the making of Nano?"},{"time":236000,"text":"Let me tell you a bit about it."},{"time":238000,"text":"For example, how we started:"},{"time":241000,"text":"Ratan just began with a five-engineer team,"},{"time":244000,"text":"young people in their mid-twenties."},{"time":247000,"text":"And he said,"},{"time":249000,"text":"\"Well, I won't define the vehicle for you,"},{"time":251000,"text":"but I will define the cost for you."},{"time":253000,"text":"It is one lakh, 100,000 rupees,"},{"time":255000,"text":"and you are to make it within that.\""},{"time":257000,"text":"And he told them,"},{"time":259000,"text":"\"Question the unquestionable."},{"time":261000,"text":"Stretch the envelope.\""},{"time":263000,"text":"And at a point in time,"},{"time":265000,"text":"he got so engrossed in the whole challenge,"},{"time":267000,"text":"that he himself became a member of the team."},{"time":269000,"text":"Can you believe it?"},{"time":271000,"text":"I still am told about this story"},{"time":273000,"text":"of that single wiper design in which he participated."},{"time":276000,"text":"Until midnight, he'd be thinking."},{"time":278000,"text":"Early morning he'll be coming back with sort of solutions."},{"time":281000,"text":"But who was the team leader?"},{"time":283000,"text":"The team leader was Girish Wagh,"},{"time":285000,"text":"a 34 year-old boy in [unclear]."},{"time":287000,"text":"And the Nano team average age"},{"time":289000,"text":"was just 27 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"And they did innovation in design and beyond."},{"time":295000,"text":"Broke many norms of the standard conventions for the first time."},{"time":298000,"text":"For example, that a two-cylinder gas engine"},{"time":301000,"text":"was used in a car with a single balancer shaft."},{"time":304000,"text":"Adhesives were replacing the rivets."},{"time":307000,"text":"There was a co-creation, a huge co-creation,"},{"time":310000,"text":"with vendors and suppliers."},{"time":312000,"text":"All ideas on board were welcome."},{"time":314000,"text":"100 vendors were co-located adjacent to the plant,"},{"time":317000,"text":"and innovative business models for automobile dealerships were developed."},{"time":320000,"text":"Imagine that a fellow"},{"time":322000,"text":"who sells cloth, for example, will be selling Nano."},{"time":325000,"text":"I mean, it was incredible innovation."},{"time":328000,"text":"Seeking solutions for non-auto sectors."},{"time":331000,"text":"It was an open innovation,"},{"time":333000,"text":"ideas from all over were welcome."},{"time":335000,"text":"The mechanism of helicopters seats and windows was used, by the way,"},{"time":338000,"text":"as well as a dashboard"},{"time":340000,"text":"that was inspired by two-wheelers."},{"time":342000,"text":"The fuel lines and lamps"},{"time":344000,"text":"were as in two-wheelers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"And the crux of the matter was, however,"},{"time":349000,"text":"getting more from less."},{"time":352000,"text":"All the time, you have been given an envelope."},{"time":354000,"text":"You can't cross that envelope,"},{"time":356000,"text":"which is 100,000 rupees, 2,000 dollars."},{"time":359000,"text":"And therefore, each component"},{"time":361000,"text":"had to have a dual functionality."},{"time":364000,"text":"And the seat riser, for example,"},{"time":366000,"text":"serving as a mounting for the seat"},{"time":368000,"text":"as well as a structural part"},{"time":370000,"text":"of the functional rigidity."},{"time":372000,"text":"Half the number of parts"},{"time":374000,"text":"are contained in Nano"},{"time":376000,"text":"in comparison to a typical passenger car."},{"time":379000,"text":"The length is smaller by eight percent by the way."},{"time":381000,"text":"But the current entry-level cars"},{"time":383000,"text":"in comparison to that is eight percent less,"},{"time":385000,"text":"but 21 percent more inside space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"And what happened"},{"time":392000,"text":"was that -- more from less --"},{"time":394000,"text":"you can see how much more for how much less."},{"time":397000,"text":"When the Model T was launched --"},{"time":399000,"text":"and this is, by the way, all the figures"},{"time":401000,"text":"that are adjusted to 2007 dollar prices --"},{"time":404000,"text":"Model T was 19,700 by Ford."},{"time":407000,"text":"Volkswagon was 11,333."},{"time":410000,"text":"And British Motor was around 11,000."},{"time":413000,"text":"And Nano was, bang, 2,000 dollars."},{"time":417000,"text":"This is why"},{"time":419000,"text":"you started"},{"time":421000,"text":"actually a new paradigm shift,"},{"time":424000,"text":"where the same people"},{"time":427000,"text":"who could not dream of sitting in a car,"},{"time":429000,"text":"who were carrying their entire family in a scooter,"},{"time":431000,"text":"started dreaming of being in a car."},{"time":434000,"text":"And those dreams are getting fulfilled."},{"time":437000,"text":"This is a photograph"},{"time":439000,"text":"of a house and a driver and a car"},{"time":441000,"text":"near my own home."},{"time":443000,"text":"The driver's name is Naran."},{"time":445000,"text":"He has bought his own Nano."},{"time":447000,"text":"And you can see, there is a physical space"},{"time":449000,"text":"that has been created for him,"},{"time":451000,"text":"parking that car, along with the owner's car,"},{"time":454000,"text":"but more importantly, they've created"},{"time":457000,"text":"a space in their mind that"},{"time":459000,"text":"\"Yes, my chauffeur is going to come in his own car and park it.\""},{"time":462000,"text":"And that's why I call it a transformational innovation."},{"time":466000,"text":"It is not just technological,"},{"time":469000,"text":"it is social innovation that we talk about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":472000,"text":"And that is where, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":475000,"text":"this famous theme"},{"time":477000,"text":"of getting more from less for more"},{"time":480000,"text":"becomes important."},{"time":482000,"text":"I remember talking about this for the first time in Australia,"},{"time":485000,"text":"about one and a half years ago,"},{"time":487000,"text":"when their academy honored me with a fellowship."},{"time":490000,"text":"And unbelievably, in 40 years,"},{"time":492000,"text":"I was the first Indian to be honored."},{"time":494000,"text":"And the title of my talk"},{"time":496000,"text":"was therefore \"Indian innovation"},{"time":498000,"text":"from Gandhi to Gandhian engineering.\""},{"time":501000,"text":"And I titled this more from less for more and more people"},{"time":504000,"text":"as Gandhian engineering."},{"time":506000,"text":"And Gandhian engineering, in my judgment,"},{"time":508000,"text":"is the one which is going to take the world forward,"},{"time":511000,"text":"is going to make a difference,"},{"time":513000,"text":"not just for a few, but for everyone."},{"time":515000,"text":"Let me move from mobility in a car to individual mobility"},{"time":518000,"text":"for those unfortunates"},{"time":520000,"text":"who have lost their legs."},{"time":522000,"text":"Here is an American citizen and his son"},{"time":525000,"text":"having an artificial foot."},{"time":527000,"text":"What is its price? 20,000 dollars."},{"time":530000,"text":"And of course, these feet are so designed"},{"time":533000,"text":"that they can walk only on"},{"time":536000,"text":"such perfect pavement or roads."}]},{"cues":[{"time":538000,"text":"Unfortunately, that's not the case in India."},{"time":541000,"text":"You can see him walk barefoot"},{"time":543000,"text":"on an awkward land, sometimes in a marshy land,"},{"time":545000,"text":"and so on and so forth."},{"time":547000,"text":"More importantly,"},{"time":549000,"text":"they not only walk far to work,"},{"time":551000,"text":"and not only do they cycle to work,"},{"time":553000,"text":"but they cycle for work, as you can see here."},{"time":556000,"text":"And they climb up for their work."},{"time":559000,"text":"You have to design an artificial foot for such conditions."},{"time":562000,"text":"A challenge, of course."},{"time":564000,"text":"Four billion people, their incomes are less then two dollars a day."},{"time":567000,"text":"And if you talk about a 20,000-dollar shoe,"},{"time":569000,"text":"you're talking about 10,000 days of income."},{"time":572000,"text":"You just don't have it."},{"time":574000,"text":"And therefore, you ought to look at alternatives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":576000,"text":"And that is how Jaipur Foot was created in India."},{"time":579000,"text":"It had a revolutionary prosthetic fitment and delivery system,"},{"time":583000,"text":"a quick molding and modular components,"},{"time":586000,"text":"enabling custom-made, on-the-spot limb fitments."},{"time":590000,"text":"You could feel it actually in an hour, by the way,"},{"time":592000,"text":"whereas the equivalent other feet"},{"time":594000,"text":"took something like a day, as so on."},{"time":596000,"text":"Outer socket made by using heated high-density polyethylene pipes,"},{"time":600000,"text":"rather than using heated sheets."},{"time":603000,"text":"And unique high-ankle design and human-like looks,"},{"time":606000,"text":"[unclear] and functions."},{"time":608000,"text":"And I like to show how it looks"},{"time":610000,"text":"and how it works."},{"time":618000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":622000,"text":"See, he jumps. You can see what stress it must have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"(Text: ... any person with a below the knee limb could do this."},{"time":627000,"text":"... above the limb, yes, it would be difficult ..."},{"time":630000,"text":"\"Did it hurt?\""},{"time":632000,"text":"\"No ... not at all.\""},{"time":643000,"text":"... he can run a kilometer in four minutes and 30 seconds ...)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":645000,"text":"One kilometer in four minutes and 30 seconds."},{"time":647000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":660000,"text":"So that's what it is all about."},{"time":662000,"text":"And therefore Time took notice"},{"time":664000,"text":"of this 28-dollar foot, basically."},{"time":666000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":669000,"text":"An incredible story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672000,"text":"Let's move on to something else."},{"time":674000,"text":"I've been talking about getting more from less for more."},{"time":676000,"text":"Let's move to health."},{"time":678000,"text":"We've talked about mobility and the rest of it, let's talk about health."},{"time":681000,"text":"What's happening in the area of health?"},{"time":683000,"text":"You know, you have new diseases that require new drugs."},{"time":686000,"text":"And if you look at the drug development 10 years ago and now,"},{"time":688000,"text":"what has happened?"},{"time":690000,"text":"10 years ago, it used to cost about a quarter billion."},{"time":692000,"text":"Today it costs 1.5 billion dollars."},{"time":696000,"text":"Time taken for moving a molecule to marketplace,"},{"time":699000,"text":"after all the human and animal testing,"},{"time":702000,"text":"was 10 years, now it is 15 years."},{"time":705000,"text":"Are you getting more drugs because you are spending more time and more money?"},{"time":708000,"text":"No, I'm sorry."},{"time":710000,"text":"We used to have 40, now they have come down to 30."},{"time":713000,"text":"So actually we are getting less from more"},{"time":715000,"text":"for less and less people."},{"time":717000,"text":"Why less and less people? Because it is so expensive,"},{"time":719000,"text":"so very few will be able to basically afford that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":723000,"text":"Let us just take an example."},{"time":725000,"text":"Psoriasis is very dreadful"},{"time":727000,"text":"disease of the skin."},{"time":729000,"text":"The cost of treatment, 20,000 dollars."},{"time":731000,"text":"1,000-dollar antibody injections under the skin, by the way,"},{"time":734000,"text":"and 20 of them."},{"time":736000,"text":"Time for development -- it took around 10 years"},{"time":738000,"text":"and 700 million dollars."},{"time":740000,"text":"Let's start in the spirit"},{"time":742000,"text":"of more from less and more for more"},{"time":744000,"text":"and start putting some targets."},{"time":747000,"text":"For example, we don't want 20,000 dollars; we don't have it."},{"time":750000,"text":"Can we do it [for] 100 dollars?"},{"time":752000,"text":"Time for development, not 10 years."},{"time":754000,"text":"We are in a hurry. Five years."},{"time":756000,"text":"Cost of development -- 300 million dollars."},{"time":758000,"text":"Sorry. I can't spend more than 10 million dollars."},{"time":760000,"text":"Looks absolutely audacious."},{"time":762000,"text":"Looks absolutely ridiculous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764000,"text":"You know something? This has been achieved in India."},{"time":767000,"text":"These targets have been achieved in India."},{"time":769000,"text":"And how they have been achieved ..."},{"time":771000,"text":"Sir Francis Bacon once said,"},{"time":773000,"text":"\"When you wish to achieve results"},{"time":775000,"text":"that have not been achieved before,"},{"time":777000,"text":"it is an unwise fancy to think"},{"time":779000,"text":"that they can be achieved by using methods"},{"time":781000,"text":"that have been used before.\""},{"time":783000,"text":"And therefore, the standard process,"},{"time":785000,"text":"where you develop a molecule, put it into mice, into men,"},{"time":787000,"text":"are not yielding those results --"},{"time":789000,"text":"the billions of dollars that have been spent."},{"time":791000,"text":"The Indian cleverness"},{"time":793000,"text":"was using its traditional knowledge,"},{"time":796000,"text":"however, scientifically validating it"},{"time":798000,"text":"and making that journey from men to mice to men,"},{"time":801000,"text":"not molecule to mice to men, you know."},{"time":803000,"text":"And that is how this difference has come."},{"time":805000,"text":"And you can see this blending"},{"time":807000,"text":"of traditional medicine, modern medicine, modern science."},{"time":809000,"text":"I launched a big program"},{"time":811000,"text":"[unclear] CSIR about nine years ago."},{"time":814000,"text":"He is giving us not just for Psoriasis,"},{"time":816000,"text":"for cancer and a whole range of things, changing the whole paradigm."},{"time":819000,"text":"And you can see this Indian Psoriasis breakthrough"},{"time":821000,"text":"obtained by this reverse form of [unclear]"},{"time":823000,"text":"by doing things differently."},{"time":825000,"text":"You can see before treatment and after treatment."},{"time":828000,"text":"This is really getting more from less for more and more people,"},{"time":831000,"text":"because these are all affordable treatments now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":834000,"text":"Let me just remind you"},{"time":837000,"text":"of what Mahatma Gandhi had said."},{"time":839000,"text":"He had said, \"Earth provides enough"},{"time":842000,"text":"to satisfy every man's need, but not every man's greed.\""},{"time":845000,"text":"So the message he was giving us"},{"time":847000,"text":"was you must get more from less and less and less"},{"time":850000,"text":"so that you can share it for more and more people,"},{"time":852000,"text":"not only the current generation,"},{"time":854000,"text":"but the future generations."},{"time":856000,"text":"And he also said, \"I would prize every invention of science"},{"time":859000,"text":"made for the benefit for all.\""},{"time":861000,"text":"So he was giving you the message that you must have it for more and more people,"},{"time":864000,"text":"not just a few people."},{"time":866000,"text":"And therefore, ladies and gentlemen,"},{"time":868000,"text":"this is the theme, getting more"},{"time":870000,"text":"from less for more."},{"time":872000,"text":"And mind you,"},{"time":874000,"text":"it is not getting just a little more for just a little less."},{"time":877000,"text":"It's not about low cost."},{"time":879000,"text":"It's about ultra-low cost."},{"time":881000,"text":"You cannot say it's a mere treatment 10,000 dollars,"},{"time":883000,"text":"but because you are poor I'll give it for 9,000."},{"time":886000,"text":"Sorry, it doesn't work. You have to give it for 100 dollars, 200 dollars."},{"time":889000,"text":"Is it possible? It has been made possible, by the way,"},{"time":892000,"text":"for certain other different reasons."},{"time":895000,"text":"So you are not talking about low cost, you are talking about ultra-low cost."},{"time":898000,"text":"You are not talking about affordability,"},{"time":900000,"text":"you are talking about extreme affordability."},{"time":902000,"text":"Because of the four billion people whose income is under two dollars a day."},{"time":906000,"text":"You're not talking exclusive innovation."},{"time":909000,"text":"You're talking about inclusive innovation."},{"time":912000,"text":"And therefore, you're not talking about incremental innovation,"},{"time":914000,"text":"you're talking about disruptive innovation."},{"time":916000,"text":"The ideas have to be such"},{"time":918000,"text":"that you think in completely different terms."},{"time":921000,"text":"And I would also add,"},{"time":923000,"text":"it is not only getting more from less for more"},{"time":925000,"text":"by more and more people, the whole world working for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":928000,"text":"I was very touched when I saw a breakthrough the other day."},{"time":931000,"text":"You know, incubators for infants, for example."},{"time":933000,"text":"They're not available in Africa."},{"time":935000,"text":"They're not available in Indian villages."},{"time":937000,"text":"And infants die."},{"time":939000,"text":"And incubator costs 2,000 dollars."},{"time":942000,"text":"And there's a 25-dollar incubator"},{"time":944000,"text":"giving that performance that had been created."},{"time":946000,"text":"And by whom?"},{"time":948000,"text":"By young students from Standford University"},{"time":951000,"text":"on an extreme affordability project that they had, basically."},{"time":954000,"text":"Their heart is in the right place, like Ratan Tata."},{"time":957000,"text":"It's not just innovation, compassion and passion --"},{"time":960000,"text":"compassion in the heart and passion in the belly."},{"time":962000,"text":"That's the new world that we want to create."},{"time":965000,"text":"And that is why the message is that of Gandhian engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":967000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, I'd like to end before time."},{"time":970000,"text":"I was also afraid of those 18 minutes."},{"time":972000,"text":"I've still one and a half to go."},{"time":974000,"text":"The message, the final message, is this:"},{"time":977000,"text":"India gave a great gift to the world."},{"time":980000,"text":"What was that?"},{"time":982000,"text":"[In the] 20th century, we gave Gandhi to the world."},{"time":985000,"text":"The 21st century gift,"},{"time":987000,"text":"which is very, very important for the whole world,"},{"time":989000,"text":"whether it is global economic meltdown,"},{"time":991000,"text":"whether it is climate change --"},{"time":993000,"text":"any problem that you talk about"},{"time":995000,"text":"is gaining more from less for more and more --"},{"time":997000,"text":"not only the current generations,"},{"time":999000,"text":"for the future generations."},{"time":1001000,"text":"And that can come only from Gandhian engineering."},{"time":1003000,"text":"So ladies and gentlemen, I'm very happy to announce,"},{"time":1006000,"text":"this gift of the 21st century"},{"time":1008000,"text":"to the world from India,"},{"time":1010000,"text":"Gandhian engineering."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1020000,"text":"Lakshmi Pratury: Thank you, Dr. Mashelkar. (R.A. Mashelkar: Thank you very much.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1023000,"text":"LP: A quick question for you."},{"time":1025000,"text":"Now, when you were a young boy in this school,"},{"time":1028000,"text":"what were your thoughts, like what did you think you could become?"},{"time":1031000,"text":"What do you think that drove you?"},{"time":1033000,"text":"Was there a vision you had? What is it that drove you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1036000,"text":"RAM: I'll tell you a story that drove me, that transformed my life."},{"time":1039000,"text":"I remember, I went to a poor school,"},{"time":1042000,"text":"because my mother could not gather the 21 rupees,"},{"time":1045000,"text":"that half a dollar that was required"},{"time":1047000,"text":"within the stipulated time."},{"time":1049000,"text":"It was [unclear] high school."},{"time":1052000,"text":"But it was a poor school with rich teachers, honestly."},{"time":1055000,"text":"And one of them was [unclear] who taught us physics."},{"time":1058000,"text":"One day he took us out into the sun"},{"time":1060000,"text":"and tried to show us how to find"},{"time":1062000,"text":"the focal length of a convex lens."},{"time":1065000,"text":"The lens was here. The piece of paper was there. He moved it up and down."},{"time":1068000,"text":"And there was a bright spot up there."},{"time":1071000,"text":"And then he said, \"This is the focal length.\""},{"time":1073000,"text":"But then he held it for a little while, Lakshmi."},{"time":1076000,"text":"And then the paper burned."},{"time":1078000,"text":"When the paper burned, for some reason he turned to me,"},{"time":1080000,"text":"and he said, \"Mashelkar, like this,"},{"time":1083000,"text":"if you do not diffuse your energies,"},{"time":1085000,"text":"if you focus your energies,"},{"time":1087000,"text":"you can achieve anything in the world.\""},{"time":1090000,"text":"That gave me a great message: focus and you can achieve."},{"time":1093000,"text":"I said, \"Whoa, science is so wonderful,"},{"time":1095000,"text":"I have to become a scientist.\""},{"time":1097000,"text":"But more importantly, focus and you can achieve."},{"time":1100000,"text":"And that message, very frankly,"},{"time":1102000,"text":"is valuable for society today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1104000,"text":"What does that focal length do?"},{"time":1107000,"text":"It has parallel lines, which are sun rays."},{"time":1110000,"text":"And the property of parallel lines"},{"time":1112000,"text":"is that they never meet."},{"time":1114000,"text":"What does that convex lens do?"},{"time":1116000,"text":"It makes them meet."},{"time":1118000,"text":"This is convex lens leadership."},{"time":1120000,"text":"You know what today's leadership is doing? Concave length."},{"time":1123000,"text":"They divide them farther."},{"time":1126000,"text":"So I learned the lesson"},{"time":1128000,"text":"of convex lens leadership from that."},{"time":1130000,"text":"And when I was at National Chemical Laboratory [unclear]."},{"time":1133000,"text":"When I was at Council of Scientific Industry Research --"},{"time":1135000,"text":"40 laboratories -- when two laboratories were not talking to each other,"},{"time":1137000,"text":"I would [unclear]."},{"time":1140000,"text":"And currently I'm president of Global Research Alliance,"},{"time":1142000,"text":"60,000 scientists in nine counties, right from India to the U.S."},{"time":1145000,"text":"I'm trying to build a global team,"},{"time":1148000,"text":"which will look at the global grand challenges that the world is facing."},{"time":1151000,"text":"That was the lesson. That was the inspirational moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1153000,"text":"LP: Thank you very much. (RAM: Thank you.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1156000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}